edu.ucla.sspace.mains
Class DependencyGenericMain

java.lang.Object
  edu.ucla.sspace.mains.GenericMain
      edu.ucla.sspace.mains.DependencyGenericMain
Direct Known Subclasses:
DependencyBasisMaker, DependencyRandomIndexingMain, DependencyVectorSpaceMain, StructuredVectorSpaceMain
public abstract class DependencyGenericMain
extends GenericMain

This abstract class extends GenericMain by overing the getDocumentIterator function such that it generates document iterators for dependency parse trees.

Author:
Keith Stevens
